  <h2 class=3D"name">Bard</h2>
  <div class=3D"text text-columns-2">

    <div>Bards are the most charismatic people in all the realms. Members o=
f this class are masters of captivation and specialize in a variety of perf=
ormance types, including singing, playing musical instruments, weaving tale=
s, or telling jokes. Whether performing for an audience or speaking to an i=
ndividual, bards thrive in social situations. Members of this profession bo=
nd and train at schools or guilds, but a current of egotism runs through th=
ose of the bardic persuasion. While they may be the most likely class to br=
ing people together, a bard of ill temper can just as easily tear a party a=
part.</div>
    <div class=3D"outlined">
      <div><strong>Domains:</strong>
